text.0: "Amazing Falcon Heavy launch from Cape Canaveral! Witnessed the most revolutionary satellite constellation taking off 🚀🛰. The view was breathtaking on the eastern seaboard! 🔭 #FalconHeavy #SpaceX #Space #Launch"
